         Traceback (most recent call last):
           File ".../routing_smoke.py", line 200, in run_one
             reply = runner(orch, prompt, on_progress)
           File ".../orchestrator/main.py", line 4511, in handle_message
             ...
         RuntimeError: unable to load model: qwen3:4b
    ============================================================

Exit code 0 = all passed. Exit code 1 = one or more failures.
